# Chronicare Blog 🩺

A multi-page responsive blog for chronic illness education and management.

## 🌐 Live Demo

Visit Site https://plp-webtechnologies.github.io/feb-2025-final-project-and-deployment-Butichiivy/

## 📁 Pages

- `index.html` – Homepage with health tips, gallery, and signup
- `about.html` – Info about the mission of Chronicare
- `contact.html` – Contact form and contact details

## ⚙️ Features

- Responsive design using Flexbox
- CSS animations and hover effects
- JavaScript interactivity (form validation, theming)
- localStorage to save theme preferences
- Semantic HTML5

## 🚀 Built With

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript
- GitHub Pages (for deployment)

